# Task Objective
After debugging and achieving 100% visual parity with the old API, ensure the new app can form the exact same identical report utilizing the *new API*.

# Detailed Steps
1. Adapt the frontend report data parser to consume the new API.
2. Ensure the resulting parsed data structure perfectly matches the structure used to render the legacy-identical view.
3. Verify that the final visual output remains identical to the screenshots across the new API integration.
